        "name": "Ares Management Limited",
        "parent": "Ares Management Corporation",
        "replacementMechanism": "The Collateral Manager may be replaced upon (i) an Event of Default by the Collateral Manager, (ii) termination by the relevant noteholders following the applicable conditions, or (iii) voluntary resignation by the Collateral Manager. Notes held by the Collateral Manager or any Collateral Manager Related Person have no voting rights for the purposes of CM Removal or Replacement Resolutions."
